==Regional Walkthroughs== ===Kanto===
Summary: Without using the [[Underground]] to mine stones and using typed eggs, 74100 Quest Points are needed. Using Mystery Eggs, Mining for stones, [[Rare hold items]], and [[Berries]] 29900 Quest Points are needed.
